items.name: SDXL Wrong LoRA
items.description:
This model was originally uploaded to Huggingface by Max Woolf - if Max would like to claim ownership of this model, please contact us.

A LoRA for SDXL 1.0 Base which improves output image quality after loading it and using wrong as a negative prompt during inference. You can demo image generation using this LoRA in this Colab Notebook.

Benefits of using this LoRA:

  • Higher detail in textures/fabrics, particularly at full 1024x1024 resolution.

  • Higher color saturation and vibrance.

  • Higher sharpness for blurry/background objects.

  • Better at anatomically-correct hands.

  • Less likely to have random artifacts.

  • Appears to allow the model to follow the input prompt with a more expected behavior, particularly with prompt weighting such as the Compel syntax.

items.name: KevaMix2.5D
items.description:
INSTRUCTION

My model's purpose is to generate images with a colorful sketch-like style or something between an anime and a realistic style, while maintaining the '2D' aspect of the anime style. I find it difficult to describe and I'm not entirely sure if the way I've described it in the preceding sentences is the perfect portrayal of the images I display to illustrate my model and that's why I wasn't inspired with the name of this model. Nonetheless, I'm sharing it because I really enjoy the images I achieve with it.

The optimal settings would be:

  • Sampler: DPM++ 2M Karras, DPM++ SDE Karras

  • Steps: 20 to 30 (I believe up to 40 would still yield good results)

  • VAE: vae-ft-ema-560000-ema-pruned.ckpt (this is the one I used, but perhaps another one might yield better results)

  • Upscaler: 4x-Ultrasharp, as it allows preserving the desired style for the images, but R-ESRGAN 4x+ Anime6B could also work equally well.

items.name: emrata SDXL LoRA
items.description:
This is my 2nd attempt at creating a LoRA for Emily Ratajkowski. 1st upload of a model ever anywhere! Need some advice on how to improve it and model training in general, so if you can help, send me a comment.

Trained on 89 Instagram photos, 10 repeats, 10 epochs, 0.001 unet training rate, ro reg images. Took about 5.5 hours on runpod. v3.0 trained the same but with 1 repeat of regularization images; seems to have helped.

May be just me, but either using the SDXL offset Lora set to weight of 0.0357 (0.0357 is the noise offset for the original training of SDXL) or using Lora weight of 1.0357 with this Lora seems to produce better results. This Lora was trained with the same noise offset. Try it out and let me know below your results.

See my training project data at https://wandb.ai/lebowski

Hope you enjoy!

Dude here

items.name: 【再世】next life-黄新
items.description:
这是群星再世第七十四期，以后会不定期出去世的群星Lora，以纪念他们。

黄新出生很早，但一直都在打零工维持生活，直到1971年，45岁的黄新才参演第一部电视剧《冷暖亲情》出道。因为长相的问题，开始只能出演一些反派，黄新开始崭露头角是在1980年与周润发合作的《上海滩》，黄新饰演的是狡诈虚伪、阴险毒辣的聂人王，他利用许文强削弱冯敬尧的力量，而许文强利用他报仇，两人互相利用。随后参演《香港八一》至《香港八六》系列喜剧，饰演“银禧小食店”老板“懋叔”一角，渐渐转型成为好人，也因为这个系列电影被观众熟悉。

黄新是属于那种典型的只要一看到照片就能想起很多老电影的演员，虽然他在电影中的镜头不多，但是独特的演技很容易让观众记住。黄新与周润发搭档的戏有很多，而且都是经典，比如1988年香港电影票房冠军《八星报喜》，饰演一个艺员培训班的老师；《吉星拱照》中饰演周润发的管家老胖，一方面要帮着周润发逃离家人的监管，另一方面要给利智饰演的表妹和两位老太太遮掩大少爷的事情；《赌神》中饰演王祖贤的父亲；还有在《精装追女仔》中饰演张敏的父亲，没有台词，只是一个傻笑的老好人。

1999年，因中风去世，享年73岁。

素材来自《吉星拱照》《精武英雄》《精装追女仔》《富贵再逼人》

items.description:
Used to generate mhy style q-version miniatures,And with other Lora.Please note that since this lora was created to be paired with other lora, a weight of 0.4 is recommended for use on its own.512-768.请注意，由于这个lora是为了和其他Lora搭配制作出来的，所以单独使用权重建议为0.4

mhy风格欠拟合

本模型用米哈游活动中的q版小人练成，触发词为bhxy3和chibi，测试模型为秋叶自带的anyv5.可以用front view调出正视图。

如果你的模型是融合模型或者画风特化如ReV和孤辰的模型又想跑出和例图一样的强烈建议用唬人版本。

欠拟合版：

q版米哈游欠拟合(mhy-chibi-artistic style) - v1.0 | Stable Diffusion LoRA | Civitai

优点是更听话，可以调用底模元素。

缺点是很容易被其他模型与lora带偏。

图都是512-768直接出图，推荐权重0.9.

clip2

测试提示词：

bhxy3,1girl,solo, short hair  , elf,  yellow hair,see-through bodysuit,full body,white background,  simple background,chibi,  

唬人版：

https://civitai.com/models/128798/used-to-generate-mhy-style-q-version-miniatures

相对过拟合的米哈游小人q版模型，

优点是无论与任何lora搭配都可以保持mhy的q版风格，也可以用任何大模型。

缺点是很难出素材之外的内容，单独使用时推荐降低权重为0.4。

不过跑裙子很好（指素材里的裙子）。

clip2

测试词：

bhxy3,1girl,solo,dress,full body,white background,  simple background,chibi ,

mhy style underfitting

This model is practiced with q-version miniatures from the Miha Tour event, the trigger words are bhxy3 and chibi, and the test model is anyv5 that comes with Autumn Leaf.You can use front view to call up the front view.

If your model is a fusion model or painting style specialization such as ReV and Lone Star's model and want to run the same as the example picture is highly recommended to use the bluff version.

Underfitting version:

q版米哈游欠拟合(mhy-chibi-artistic style) - v1.0 | Stable Diffusion LoRA | Civitai

The advantage is that it is more obedient and can call the underlying model elements.

The disadvantage is that it is easy to be biased by other models with lora.

The graphs are all 512-768 straight out of the box, with a recommended weight of 0.9.

clip2

Test cue words:

https://civitai.com/models/128798/used-to-generate-mhy-style-q-version-miniatures

bhxy3,1girl,solo, short hair , elf, yellow hair,see-through bodysuit,full body,white background, simple background,chibi,

Bluffing version:

A relatively overfitted q-version model of the Mihaou villain.

Pros are that you can keep the q version style of mhy no matter with any lora, and you can also use any big model.

The disadvantage is that it's hard to get out beyond the material, and it's recommended to lower the weight to 0.4 when used alone.

Runs skirts well though (meaning the skirts in the material).

clip2

Test words:

bhxy3,1girl,solo,dress,full body,white background, simple background,chibi ,

items.name: Jeanne d'Arc (Archer)
items.description:
Someone requested this LORA, and I did it because I personally wanted one too. I saw some that weren't convincing enough (Quality over quantity, if ya ass doesn't know the character dont even bother training a bad LORA model that is inconsistent), so I took matters into my own hands.

I'd like to first apologize because the third ascension is currently not available. There aren't many good images that even meet the minimum requirements to train the model. The available art is either bad or inconsistent with the official art.

There is a model from the official Fate Grand Order Arcade that I might use to train the Lora, but I don't know if it contains the necessary bones for posing. If anyone finds a good rigged model of her, let me know.

So only two versions are available, the first and second ascension. Both are very flexible in terms of clothing. I will add the recommended tags for each version.

Both were trained with around 150+ images, each one very carefully picked. They work fine with anime checkpoints. I tried some real-life models, but the results are not as good. Mostly, the face is left without her iconic hair on her forehead

Examples here were generated using a variety of different checkpoints; AnyLora, Anime Screenshot-like Style, AnyHentai, DarkRevPikas, Grapefruit.

Highly recommend the use of hires fix and ADetailer.

Works perfect at strength 1 but feel free to experiment.

That's it, enjoy this LORA, think it turned out real nice.

Blanca Martínez Suárez (born 21 October 1988) is a Spanish actress. She is best known for her performances on television series The Boarding School (2007–10), The Boat (2011–13), and the Spanish Language Netflix series' Las chicas del cable (English: Cable Girls) (2017–2020) and Jaguar (2021-).

She has also worked with Pedro Almodóvar in films as The Skin I Live In (2011), which earned her a Goya Award nomination as Best New Actress, and I'm So Excited! (2013).
